<p>&#8220;I want make cool friends, and I&#8217;m starting a Candor Club as the venue.  I don’t know how to advertise it well, so you&#8217;re going to have to settle for this hand-out.  I have no idea where to hold the meeting, so just join me at ~landmark~ ~time~  and we&#8217;ll figure out where to go.&#8221;</p>

<p>Then put the hand-outs everywhere &#8212; bulletin boards, lavatories, whatever.</p>

